+++# CODEX_TESTING.md — RustyBMP Automated Test Runbook
+++# Replaces: docs/UBUNTU_TESTING.md (deprecated)
+++# All commands run from repo root on Ubuntu 24.04.
+++
+++## Prerequisites (one-time)
